
function add(a,b){}
here a,b is know as paramenters

add(a,b); => here a,b is known as arguments
when we call a function that process is known as function invokation

in javaScript functions are known as first class citizens MEANS => you can create functions as variables in JS
example:-
let add = function(a,b){
  return a+b;
}

